OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright
OL,6,Fevening for most with some late
OL,7,Fsunshine. Overnight remaining dry with
OL,8,Fplenty of clear skies, although a few
OL,9,Fshowers may move west along the south
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA dry and sunny day for
OL,13,Fmuch of the region, however parts of
OL,14,FCornwall and west Devon may see some
OL,15,Fshowers at times. A windy day with
OL,16,Fcoastal gales possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
