OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry,
OL,6,Fwarm and sunny again for many on
OL,7,FThursday and Friday but some showers
OL,8,Fpossible towards Cornwall. Winds
OL,9,Fturning lighter later on Thursday.
OL,10,FCloudier on Saturday.
